    Completing Territory Three journey, preparing to return through Territory Two tomorrow. Journey has taught Kira real skills but she's still waiting for Elder Heartwood's "real" answer about survival. Hopeful and confident that ancient wisdom will solve what the journey couldn't. Chapter ends with anticipation building - what will Elder Heartwood say?
